
Overview of noun rain

The noun rain has 3 senses (first 2 from tagged texts)
                                           
1. (25) rain, rainfall -- (water falling in drops from vapor condensed in the atmosphere)
2. (5) rain, rainwater -- (drops of fresh water that fall as precipitation from clouds)
3. rain, pelting -- (anything happening rapidly or in quick successive; "a rain of bullets"; "a pelting of insults")

